[SPEAKER_03]: side, if you will.

394
00:42:57,078 --> 00:42:57,598
[SPEAKER_03]: A question.

395
00:42:59,219 --> 00:43:06,021
[SPEAKER_11]: Yeah, what what happens if you have more than one moving vehicle that comes in at one time?

396
00:43:07,982 --> 00:43:09,402
[SPEAKER_05]: Yeah, so that that's a great question.

397
00:43:09,442 --> 00:43:12,643
[SPEAKER_05]: It really gets to the management of of, you know.

398
00:43:14,083 --> 00:43:19,265
